{"tid":2048210,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟通哩篇新聞稿想點？","createTime":"2020-06-02T15:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T15:38:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e19bd6bff3bd4e3112c1ca54e0593b3c08f7e152","tid":2048210,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"標題否認但內文不斷吹風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中概股回港】拼多多否認回港第二上市　平版淘寶投資界極看好<br />\n<br />\n騰訊新聞報導，拼多多（PDD）確定回港第二上市，並確定中金為保薦人之一，知情人士透露，拼多多上市團隊原定於６月中旬交按，但不排除加快進度，但暫時未有具體上市時間表。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，已有多隻美國上市的中概股來港上市，如京東、網易及今次的拼多多，在三隻中概股當中，或許香港人對拼多多不太熟悉，因拼多多沒有海外業務，但其實不少投資界都對其潛力非常樂觀。⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2659759/【中概股回港】拼多多否認回港第二上市%E3%80%80平版淘寶投資界極看好\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2659759%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E6%A6%82%E8%82%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E6%8B%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%25E3%2580%2580%E5%B9%B3%E7%89%88%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%95%8C%E6%A5%B5%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=d64f65c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2659759/【中概股回港】拼多多否認回港第二上市%E3%80%80平版淘寶投資界極看好</a>"},{"pid":"46009d139c704327810cc9420c1c75e467d9b81d","tid":2048210,"uid":153151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"888c3b8e32681671cbfec353c78672d6aacc506b","tid":2048210,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy